import React from "react";
import {
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  Container,
  Col,
} from "reactstrap";

const LoginComponent = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <form onSubmit={this.props.handleSubmit}>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col md={6}>
            <FormGroup>
              <Col md={6}>
                <Label for="username" className="mr-sm-2">
                  Username
                </Label>
                <Input
                  type="text"
                  name="username"
                  id="username"
                  placeholder="Username"
                />
              </Col>
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>

          <Col md={6}>
            <FormGroup>
              <Col md={6}>
                <Label for="Password" className="mr-sm-2">
                  Password
                </Label>
                <Input
                  type="password"
                  name="password"
                  id="Password"
                  placeholder="Password"
                />
              </Col>
            </FormGroup>
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
      </form>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default LoginComponent;
